==气象历史==
{{storm path|Daniel 2006 track.png}}
7月2日，丹尼爾起源於[[非洲|非洲]]西岸的一股[[东风波|东风波]]。該東風波橫过[[大西洋|大西洋]]和[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]，並帶有少許相關的{{link-en|对流 (气象)|convection (meteorology)|对流}}，它在7月12日橫越[[中美洲|中美洲]]进入東[[太平洋|太平洋]]。其对流在7月13日加强，系统于两天后在[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]以南展現出热带气旋发展的迹象<ref name="tcr">{{cite web|author=Jack Beven|year=2006|title=Hurricane Daniel Tropical Cyclone Report|publisher=[[National_Hurricane_Center|National Hurricane Center]]|accessdate=2007-07-18|url=https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP052006_Daniel.pdf|format=PDF|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929132956/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP052006_Daniel.pdf|archivedate=2015-09-29}}</ref>。系统以每小時25公里的速度向西移動，其組織在7月16日有所改善<ref name="716two">{{cite web|author=Stewart & Rhome |year=2006 |title=July 16 Tropical Weather Outlook |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2007-07-18 |url=ftp://ftp.met.fsu.edu/pub/weather/tropical/Outlook-P/2006071616.ABPZ20 }}{{dead link|date=April 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。在低層環流附近有相關的對流[[雨帶|雨帶]]下，估计東風波在7月16日晚上发展成热带低气压<ref name="disc1">{{cite web|author=Beven|year=2006|title=Tropical Depression Five-E Discussion One|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2007-07-29|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.001.shtml?|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016203254/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.001.shtml|archivedate=2012-10-16}}</ref>。这时其位于[[曼萨尼约|曼萨尼约]]西南偏南方约845公里<ref name="tcr"/>。

歸类为第五{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压後，系统在中層[[高壓脊|高壓脊]]的引導气流下向西移动<ref name="disc1" />。低气压形成后的几小时里，其中心附近缺乏集中的深层对流。情况对热带气旋的{{link-en|熱帶氣旋旋生|Tropical cyclogenesis|发展}}很有利，包括温暖的[[海洋表面温度|海洋表面温度]]，非常少的[[风切变|风切变]]以及气旋上已经形成的[[反气旋|反气旋]]<ref name="disc2">{{cite web|author=Pasch|year=2006|title=Tropical Depression Five-E Discussion Two|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2007-07-29|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.002.shtml?|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016203304/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.002.shtml|archivedate=2012-10-16}}</ref>。之后对流变得更加集中，以及上层[[外流_(氣象學)|流出]]的改善重合。根据[[德沃夏克分析法|德沃夏克分析法]]，氣號在[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]7月17日中午12点强化为热带风暴丹尼尔<ref name="disc3">{{cite web|author=Stewart|year=2006|title=Tropical Storm Daniel Discussion Three|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2007-07-29|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.003.shtml?|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016203314/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.003.shtml|archivedate=2012-10-16}}</ref>。之后丹尼尔的結構很快便有所改善，展现出更多的雷暴活动和[[雨带|带状特征]]<ref name="disc5">{{cite web|author=Mainelli & Avila|year=2006|title=Tropical Storm Daniel Discussion Five|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2007-07-29|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.005.shtml?|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016203326/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.005.shtml|archivedate=2012-10-16}}</ref>。系统中心发展出[[中心密集雲團|中心密集雲團]]，环流中心有明确的雨带圍绕<ref name="disc6">{{cite web|author=Pasch|year=2006|title=Tropical Storm Daniel Discussion Six|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2007-07-29|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.006.shtml?|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016203332/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.006.shtml|archivedate=2012-10-16}}</ref>。随着系统形戍[[風眼|眼状特征]]<ref name="disc8">{{cite web|author=Rhome & Stewart|year=2006|title=Hurricane Daniel Discussion Eight|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2007-07-29|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.008.shtml?|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016203426/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.008.shtml|archivedate=2012-10-16}}</ref>，[[國家颶風中心_(美國)|国家飓风中心]]在7月18日晚上将丹尼尔升级为飓风，當时候其位於[[卡沃聖盧卡斯|卡沃聖盧卡斯]]西南偏南約1420公里<ref name="tcr"/>。

[[Image:Danielpeakrgb.gif|right]]
7月19日，丹尼尔的风眼在卫星图像上变得更为明显<ref name="disc11">{{cite web|author=Stewart and Brown|year=2006|title=Hurricane Daniel Discussion Eleven|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2007-12-28|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.011.shtml?|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016203631/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.011.shtml|archivedate=2012-10-16}}</ref>，其後發展成一个[[风眼|针孔式風眼]]<ref name="disc12">{{cite web|author=Stewart and Brown|year=2006|title=Hurricane Daniel Discussion Twelve|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2007-12-28|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.012.shtml?|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016203704/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.012.shtml|archivedate=2012-10-16}}</ref>。风暴進入[[眼牆置換循環|眼牆置換循環]]並转向西北偏西方移动，其强化趋势暂时停止，之后在7月20日快速加强并达到[[热带气旋等级|大型飓风標準]]<ref name="tcr"/>。当天晚上，飓风丹尼尔组织成一个非常对称的气旋，其中心有一个非常明显，直径约为50公里的风眼。达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]的四级標準后，气旋的外观与[[环形飓风|环形飓风]]相似<ref name="disc16">{{cite web|author=Brown|year=2006|title=Hurricane Daniel Discussion Sixteen|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2007-12-28|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.016.shtml?|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016203826/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.016.shtml|archivedate=2012-10-16}}</ref>，环形飓风的特点是擁有巨大而对称的风眼，周围有厚厚的环形强对流包围，通常能够保持其强度和结构达数天之久<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.ssec.wisc.edu/~kossin/articles/annularhurr.pdf|title=Annular Hurricanes|accessdate=2009-02-28|last=Knaff|first=John A.|author2=J.P. Kossin|author3=M. DeMaria|date=April 2003|format=PDF|volume=18|work=Weather and Forecasting|publisher=American Meteorological Society|pages=204–223|bibcode=2003WtFor..18..204K|doi=10.1175/1520-0434(2003)018<0204:AH>2.0.CO;2|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070108062105/http://www.ssec.wisc.edu/~kossin/articles/annularhurr.pdf|archivedate=2007-01-08|journal=}}</ref>。7月21日，飓风进入另一次眼墙置换循環。在周期完成后，丹尼爾在7月22日早上达到每小时240公里的最高风速。此风速保持约18小时后，丹尼尔进入了一片水温逐漸转凉的海域，强度开始逐渐减弱<ref name="tcr" />。7月23日，风眼变得更为明显<ref name="disc27">{{cite web|author=Brown & Stewart|year=2006|title=Hurricane Daniel Discussion Twenty-Seven|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2007-12-28|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.027.shtml?|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016235549/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.027.shtml|archivedate=2012-10-16}}</ref>，之后风速下降，云顶再次回暖<ref name="disc28">{{cite web|author=Brown & Stewart|year=2006|title=Hurricane Daniel Discussion Twenty-Eight|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2007-12-28|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.028.shtml?|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016235557/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep05/ep052006.discus.028.shtml|archivedate=2012-10-16}}</ref>。

飓风在7月24日进入[[中太平洋飓风中心|中太平洋飓风中心]]的预报责任区<ref name="tcr"/>，此時其风眼消失在卫星图像上。原本预计丹尼尔将以热带风暴標準横过夏威夷群島，因为該群岛附近海域的水温较高<ref name="disc31">{{cite web|author=Houston|year=2006|title=Hurricane Daniel Discussion Thirty-One|publisher=Central Pacific Hurricane Center|accessdate=2007-12-28|url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCDCP1.EP052006.31.0607241510|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110518213256/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2006/TCDCP1.EP052006.31.0607241510|archivedate=2011-05-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而预计风切变亦是微弱<ref name="cphc">{{cite web|publisher=Central Pacific Hurricane Center|year=2006|title=Overview of the 2006 Central North Pacific Tropical Cyclone Season|accessdate=2007-12-28|url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/summaries/2006.php#daniel|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080103013712/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/summaries/2006.php#daniel|archivedate=2008-01-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，風暴因北面的高壓脊減弱而減速，以及在水温较低和东风切变增强的共同影響下，丹尼尔在7月25日减弱为热带风暴<ref name="tcr"/>。当天晚上，外露的环流中心附近已经没有活跃的对流，系统在7月26日早上減弱为热带低气压。由于雷暴活动也未能重新发展，丹尼尔于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]7月27日凌晨0時退化成残留[[低气压|低气压]]，残留低气压继续向西北偏西方移动，在7月28日於[[夏威夷島|夏威夷大岛]]东南方消散<ref name="cphc"/>。

==防災措施和影响==
[[Image:TD_Daniel_(2006).JPG|right]]
由于起初预测飓风丹尼尔将以热带风暴標準橫越夏威夷群岛，[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]]和[[夏威夷县|夏威夷县]]的官员建议居民准备飓风应急包裹，他們还建议购买不易变壞的食物和电池。这候，风暴距该離州可能受影响的地区还有数天，結果只有很少居民立即准备<ref>{{cite web|author=Rod Thomson|date=2006-07-25|title=Weakening Hurricane Daniel still a concern for Big Isle|publisher=''Honolulu Star-Bulletin''|accessdate=2007-12-29|url=http://archives.starbulletin.com/2006/07/25/news/story01.html|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120826000647/http://archives.starbulletin.com/2006/07/25/news/story01.html|archivedate=2012-08-26}}</ref>。[[檀香山|檀香山]][[国家气象局_(美国)|国家气象局]]对夏威夷东面海滩发布高海浪预警，警告在沙滩上的人不要下水<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[National_Aeronautics_and_Space_Administration|National Aeronautics and Space Administration]]|year=2006|title=Hurricane Season 2006: Daniel (Eastern Pacific)|accessdate=2007-12-29|url=http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/hurricanes/archives/2006/h2006_daniel.html|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019234424/http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/hurricanes/archives/2006/h2006_daniel.html|archivedate=2012-10-19}}</ref>。美国国家气象局对丹尼尔的残余发布[[暴洪|暴洪]]观測预警和强风警告<ref>{{cite web|author=Honolulu National Weather Service|year=2006|title=July 2006 Tropical Weather Statements|accessdate=2007-12-29|url=http://elists.pdc.org/pipermail/emops/2006-July.txt|format=TXT|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120209180626/http://elists.pdc.org/pipermail/emops/2006-July.txt|archivedate=2012-02-09|df=}}</ref>。

7月28至29日，丹尼尔的残余為[[夏威夷岛|夏威夷大岛]]和[[茂宜島|茂宜島]]的向风区域带来50至125[[毫米|毫米]]降雨量<ref name="cphc"/>。茂宜島上的西威鲁埃基（{{lang|en|West Wailuaiki}}）在一天內记录了98.3毫米的降雨量，是飓风带来单日降水量最高的地方<ref>{{cite web|author=Kevin R. Kodama|year=2006|title=July 2006 Hawaii Precipitation Summary|publisher=Honolulu National Weather Service|accessdate=2007-12-29|url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/hnl/hydro/pages/jul06sum.php|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060929013413/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/hnl/hydro/pages/jul06sum.php|archivedate=2006-09-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。风暴也為东茂宜岛的[[分水岭|分水岭]]带来降水<ref>{{cite news|author=Edwin Tanji|date=2006-07-29|title=Trades dissipate remnants of Daniel |publisher=''Maui News''}}</ref>。特别是在夏威夷大岛[[凱盧阿－科納|凱盧阿－科納]]的降雨造成道路{{link-en|积水|Ponding}}，小溪也出现泛滥。不过没有任何重大损失和人员伤亡的报道<ref>{{cite web |publisher=National Climatic Data Center |year=2006 |title=Event Report for Hawaii |accessdate=2007-12-29 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~608928 |archivedate=2012-01-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120112162212/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~608928 }}</ref>。一个位于{{link-en|嘉萊 (夏威夷州)|Ka Lae|嘉萊}}的气象站簡要地报告持续风速约为每小时56公里，阵风每小时72公里<ref name="cphc"/>。

第61届跨部门飓风会议期间，夏威夷州民防部请求将“丹尼尔”（{{lang|en|Daniel}}）这个名稱[[除名太平洋飓风名称列表|除名]]，理由是它带来很大的威胁或损失，讓人難以忘記<ref>{{cite web |publisher=Interdepartmental Hurricane Conference |year=2007 |title=The Nation's Hurricane Program: An Interagency Success Story |accessdate=2007-12-29 |url=http://www.ofcm.gov/ihc07/web-61st-IHC-Booklet.pdf |format=PDF |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5f9vkkp2f?url=http://www.ofcm.gov/ihc07/web-61st-IHC-Booklet.pdf |archivedate=2009-03-10 |df= }}</ref>，但[[世界气象组织|世界气象组织]]並没有同意这项请求<ref>{{cite web|author=Dennis H. McCarthy|year=2007|title=National Weather Service Instruction Tropical Cyclone Names and Pronunciation Guide|accessdate=2007-12-29|url=http://www.weather.gov/directives/sym/pd01006006curr.pdf|format=PDF|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080910161627/http://www.weather.gov/directives/sym/pd01006006curr.pdf|archivedate=2008-09-10|df=}}</ref>。

